[Student "S"]
{SOUTH has 22 points and opens 2\C.

NORTH is pretty weak, right? She responds 2\D.

SOUTH bids his suit, 2\H.

NORTH is so weak she bids the second negative - 3\C.

SOUTH rebids his suit, 3\H, and NORTH passes.}

